                        <img width="966" height="719" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models.webp" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="How Attribution Models Can Boost Your Marketing Strategies - TrueProfit" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models.webp 966w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models-300x223.webp 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models-768x572.webp 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models-400x298.webp 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/attribution-models-800x595.webp 800w" sizes="(max-width: 966px) 100vw, 966px" />                    </div>
                    
                                        

